&lt;li&gt;Lead multiple teams and workstreams across scalability, reliability, modernization, compliance readiness, observability, and platform simplification.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own platform SLOs and drive measurable improvements in availability, latency, error rates, incident frequency, infrastructure efficiency, and internal partner integration reliability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prioritize the portfolio of work within the domain using clear tradeoffs across business dependency, operational risk, technical debt, compliance exposure, internal partner impact, and long-term platform health.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and lead a high-performing organization by strengthening manager capability, clarifying ownership, creating effective operating mechanisms, and reducing single points of failure across people, systems, and processes.&lt;/li&gt;
